These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
House: art-deco, townhouse, palace, gothic-revival
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. House:art-deco is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and House:townhouse##2
4. House:gothic-revival is on the far left##1
5. House:palace is between House:townhouse and House:art-deco##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| House   | gothic-revival         | townhouse   | palace | art-deco       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

