.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Pet: lizard, chinchilla, bird, dog
1. Pet:dog is between Hobby:reading and Pet:chinchilla##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Pet:bird is on the right of Pet:lizard##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Pet:lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Pet   | chinchilla    | dog   | lizard | bird       |

