3. Game:mah-jongg is on the far left##1
4. Game:chess is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == Game:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Game   | mah-jongg | backgammon   | chess | go |

